Expression Browser:
===================

The Expression browser to execute queries, view your Prometheus configuration, and Prometheus targets.

open prometheus server using browser
click on "Graph" ---> select "insert metric at cursor" search "container_cpu_load_average_10s" ---> click "execute" ---> click on "graph" to see graph

Container CPU load average:
----------------------------
container_cpu_load_average_10s

Memory usage query:
--------------------
((sum(node_memory_MemTotal_bytes) - sum(node_memory_MemFree_bytes) - sum(node_memory_Buffers_bytes) - sum(node_memory_Cached_bytes)) / sum(node_memory_MemTotal_bytes)) * 100